🚨 Important real-world considerations

🔐 On-Prem API access

Lambda must reach your on-prem API:

* VPN / Direct Connect
* Or expose API securely (not public without auth)

⸻

⏱ Timeout settings

* Increase Lambda timeout (e.g., 30–60 sec)

⸻

📦 Dependencies

For Lambda:

* Package requests library
* Or use Lambda Layer

⸻

✅ Final takeaway

* ✔ Fully dynamic query → handled via request params
* ✔ Works with any backend (Snowflake / on-prem API)
* ✔ Smart handling:
    * small → direct response
    * large → S3 + pre-signed URL
* ✔ Easily callable from your Java Kubernetes service

